parameters:
Hey, did you hear? The talk about the young lady from the
Lira family....

Ah... That thing. I heard rumors about it, but... um, is it
true...?

That girl's father... um, the talk about him... committing
suicide....

Yeah, it seems serious. \. I heard it from a child who works
under the Lira family.... \! They said that all the work was
canceled too.

All the rumors about the Kingdom's Protection were true...
It's somehow really pitiful, isn't it...

But, you know, wasn't Lunaroa quite close with that young
lady? I've seen them studying together before.
Why didn't Lunaroa... \! Give in and lose?

Well...? We can't understand the thoughts of the genius-
sama, can we? Honestly, I can't believe we're the same
species.

Ah... Isn't that the Black Uniform? It's super rare to have
two people in the same grade.

Maybe they crushed it because they didn't like that it was
taking away the special feeling and was bothersome?
Otherwise, they wouldn't have gone that far, right?

It feels possible, but scary.... Genius-sama is on a
different level.... \! It feels like we live in different
worlds.
